Affected Items: Weapons, Armor, Iron/Steel Ingots.
Cause: General Tullius has ordered all smiths to prioritize Legion contracts.
Gameplay Impact: High-quality steel is "Reserved for the Legion." Players must pay a Bribe (Guile check) or a premium to access Military-grade gear.

